Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:10.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,開いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:18.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだろう　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:19.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:21.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,動かないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何の機械だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そもそも　何なんだろうね　ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人が住む場所じゃなさそうだし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:28.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かの工場にも見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,黒い板ばっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,変な場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　一番変なのはあれだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この機械？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　持ってきたの？それ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かに使えるかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,使えないだろう　そんなんの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:52.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっかー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:58.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,変だっていうのは　壁一面にあるあの引き出し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほとんどはぴったり閉じて開けられないし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,開いていても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,中が空のやつは最初から何も入ってないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かが持っていったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かあっても大したものは入ってないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうなんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今まで入ってたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:40.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さっきの変な機械　空の薬莢　布切れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:41.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ボタン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,みたいな感じです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,って　全部持ってきたんかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かに使えるかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,使えないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっかー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かに使えるかと思ったんだけどなー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,布の切れ端を何に使うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:21.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,役にも立たない　価値もなさそうなものが大事にしまってある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何なんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,見覚えがあるやつが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,謎の石像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　カメラカメラ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,久しぶりだなー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,好きだなー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:13.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だって　形がいいし　なんか和むし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カメラっていいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,撮っておくと忘れないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カナザワに感謝だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カナザワって…誰だっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　そのカメラをくれた人だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,思い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カメラがなかったら忘れてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとうカメラ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.71,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,普通はそんな簡単に忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,元気にしてるかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,このカメラがある限り　カナザワのことは忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,死んだみたいに言うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　生きてても死んでても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう会うことはなさそうだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,イシイとかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　難しいだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしたら　いつか忘れちゃいそう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういうことか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,見て　ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,小さくて見過ごしてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どの引き出しにも名前が書いてある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これはきっと中身の持ち主なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:56.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　ここに入っているものは　その人たちが忘れてったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,忘れてったというか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,忘れられないように入れてあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここは墓なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:09.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,墓…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:21.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっとこの名前と持ち物を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かに覚えておいてもらうための目印にしたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:32.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　私たちみたいに通りかかる人もいなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,世界に誰もいなくなったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰が覚えているんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それはほら　こいつがいるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そのための石像か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雪が強くなってきたね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また寒くなるなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻しとかないと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さっきユーが拾ってきたやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれはここにないと意味がないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと場所分かるかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　これここでいいんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　どこでも一緒でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ダメだって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,びっくりしたー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,古くなった支柱が落ちてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この足場は大丈夫だろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫しか言わないよな　ユーは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこに危険が潜んでるか分からないんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:13.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか何もかもが危険すぎて　逆に大丈夫に思えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,意味が分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,塔の外に付いていた昇降機は壊れてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,代わりに道があってよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,前に登ったやつより細いよね　この塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,種類が違うのかもしれないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は昇降機に乗るより　こっちの道の方がいいけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな宙ぶらりんはごめんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもさー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:50.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全然たどり着かないね　上層に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ぐるぐる　ぐるぐる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:11:01.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,果たして登っているのか　それとも降りているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや登ってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:09.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだか　これだけ同じ場所をぐるぐる移動してるだけだと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:15.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつもの代わり映えしない日々も恋しくなってくるな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:22.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　早く登り切って　いつもの毎日に戻ろうよー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,動けば動くほど危険も増えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:34.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんは高い所に来るとすぐ弱気になるからなー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,死ぬのが怖くて生きられるかよぉー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,迷言だな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,「迷う」方のな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこまで続くんだ　この道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:18.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかこっちまで頭がぐるぐるしてきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:26.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　螺旋がぐるぐる　頭もぐるぐる…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:24.81,TEXT-JP-UP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:25.98,TEXT-JP-UP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　ストップ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ストップ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,道が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　あそこに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,出口？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,迂回路かー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かが作ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで外側に作ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人が通るのには問題なさそうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつ重いからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから登るのは嫌なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　死ぬのがこわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かった　言わなくていいから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:07.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　アクセルー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:07.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まさか　この道がこんなに愛おしく感じられるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上層への入り口だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここから上層か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,またいつもの平坦な道に戻ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,暗いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,寝て起きて　食べて移動して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:33.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また寝て
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,考えたらこれも毎日ぐるぐるだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,生きるとは　つまり螺旋のことだったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:49.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ぐるぐる回って　一体どこにたどり着くんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:14.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月が見える夜ってさあ　なんかテンション上がるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,使えそうなものは何もないな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,テンション上がるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　聞いてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,聞いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんはいつも不機嫌だよねー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に不機嫌ではないけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユーもまじめに探してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おっ　いい棒発見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:01.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だろう　不思議な力を感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これが月の魔力ってやつなのかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,魔力ね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:38.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,けっこう家が残ってるから　何かあるかなと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もないね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ボロボロだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,明るい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月光が差し込んでるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:10.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月光パワー全開ぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:13.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月光　月光　月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.18,TEXT-JP-UP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月光　月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　落ち着けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:27.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いたっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　棒拾うのやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ガラスの容器だな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空かな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,入ってるのもあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おっ　これも入ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部で３つか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が入ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水かな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ　なんて書いてあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:23.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,び…びうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,固い栓だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,開いた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい　金色の水だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかきらきらしてるねー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:49.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　ガラスの入れ物って持ってなかったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あったと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:57.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:03.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで　月光が溶け込んでるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,不思議な香りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:14.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,苦いような　甘いような
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,シュワシュワして　変な感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　もう１本開けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　ちゃんと考えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.83,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,-ユー　-何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんがおかしくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユーの顔はよく伸びるなー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これが月の魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱりあの水に月の光が溶けているのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月の光ー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:58.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつかずーっと高く登ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月に行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいね　月かー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:07.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どんな所だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:17.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,髪の毛食べないでよー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:22.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,頭痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.77,0:00:10.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.55,0:00:18.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.20,0:00:19.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.07,0:00:21.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是要转这个吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没反应呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么机器啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,话说 这里到底是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看着也不像是人住的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.68,0:02:28.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也不像是工厂
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到处都是黑色的板
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这地方真奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 最奇怪的还是那个
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这个机器吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是说这个
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 你带来了？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉会派上用场
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那种东西 派不上什么用场吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.84,0:02:52.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.68,0:02:58.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我觉得奇怪的 是整面整面墙的抽屉
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,基本都被锁上了 根本打不开
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,然后那些开着的空抽屉
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又是一开始就空着
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还是里面的东西已经被拿走了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就算里面有东西 也不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要说被我们找到的东西…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.16,0:03:40.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有刚才那奇怪的机器 空弹壳 碎布
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.31,0:03:41.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有纽扣
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就这些了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你全都留着了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,总觉得会派上用场
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你想多了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我还以为会有用上的时候呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一块破布能有什么用
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.27,0:04:21.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没什么用处 也没什么价值的东西被悉心保管着
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,前面有个熟悉的家伙
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,迷之石像
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 照相机照相机
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好久没见到了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你还真喜欢这石像啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.85,0:05:13.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为它很好看 而且让人看着就觉得平静啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,照相机真是个好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,拍下来就不会忘记了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,得感谢金泽啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,金泽是谁来着？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 是送我们照相机的人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要不是有照相机 我都要忘了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 照相机
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.71,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一般人哪有那么容易忘记啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不知道他过得怎么样了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只有还有这相机 我就不会忘记他的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别说得好像他已经死了一样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 不管他活着还是死了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们估计都没机会再见到他了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,石井也一样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊 很难再见面了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一直不见的话 没准哪天就把他们给忘了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为字太小 之前都没注意到
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,其实每个抽屉上都写有名字
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这一定是物品主人的名字
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.76,0:06:56.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那会在这里面的 都是被他们给忘了的东西吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是忘在里面的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是为了不忘记才放在里面的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这里是墓地
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.97,0:07:09.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,墓地…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.88,0:07:21.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我觉得 这里的名字和物品
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,多数是为了让别人记住而留下的标记
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.69,0:07:32.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 如果没有了像我们这样的过路人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,如果世界上不再有哪怕一个人…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有谁会记得呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你看 不是还有这家伙在吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以才造了石像吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,雪越下越大了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又要变冷了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还是放回去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是你刚才捡到的那些
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只有留在这里 它们才有意义
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还能找到原来的抽屉吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 这个是该放这里吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不管了 反正放哪里都一样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,吓死了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,老化的支柱掉下来了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这地面不会走着走着就塌了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别只会说这句话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这个世界其实充满着危险
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.00,0:10:13.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就因为一切都很危险 我反而觉得没必要太担心
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没想到除了塔外坏掉的电梯
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有别的路能走呢 真好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉这座塔比之前那座要细啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,大概不是一种类型的塔吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比起电梯 我更喜欢走这条路
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再也不想在天上晃来晃去了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.89,0:10:50.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这条路完全看不到头啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,转啊转 转啊转
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.99,0:11:01.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们究竟是在往上爬呢 还是在往下走呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,显然是在往上爬
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.89,0:11:09.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但像这样一直在同样的地方转啊转
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.08,0:11:15.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,都让人有点怀念起平时那无聊的生活了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.92,0:11:22.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那就快点爬上去 赶紧回归平时的生活吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可越往上爬就越危险
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.84,0:11:34.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你每次都这样 一到高的地方就变得胆小起来
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怕死还怎么活
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真是句名言啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只不过带引号
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这条路怎么这么长啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.84,0:12:18.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我已经彻底被这条路带晕了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.64,0:12:26.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这条路在转 我的脑子也在转…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.85,0:12:24.81,TEXT-CN-UP 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.88,0:12:25.98,TEXT-CN-UP 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 停车
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,路断了…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不 你看那边
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,出口？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,绕上去的路啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是其他人造的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么要建在外面啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,人走是没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那家伙就太重了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以我才讨厌往高处爬
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 怕死还…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,知道了 不用再说了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.32,0:14:07.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 加速
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.78,0:15:07.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没想到突然之间 我就喜欢上了这条路
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是通往上层的入口
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,从这开始就是上层了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又回到平地了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是有点黑
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,睡觉 睁眼 吃饭 上路
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.29,0:15:33.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,走累了再睡
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也许 我们的生活就跟转圈差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所谓生活 就是活在螺旋之中
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.45,0:15:49.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,转到最后 到底有什么在等着我们呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.16,0:16:14.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这种有月光的夜晚 真让人有些激动啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看来没什么能用的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真让人激动啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 你在听吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千你怎么总是一脸不高兴
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我才没有不高兴
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,拜托你也认真找找好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,找到根不错的棍子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.06,0:17:01.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么 我感觉到了一股神奇的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这就是月亮的魔力吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,魔力啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.40,0:17:38.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看见这里留有不少房子 还以为能找到些有用的东西呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,其实什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好破啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好亮
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月光射进来了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.64,0:18:10.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月光魔力全开
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.24,0:18:13.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月光 月光 月光…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.18,TEXT-CN-UP 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月光 月光…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你冷静一下
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.23,0:18:27.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别再捡棍子玩了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是玻璃容器
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,空的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也有不是空的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这瓶也不是空的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一共有3瓶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,里面装了什么东西呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,会是水吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这上面写了什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.23,0:19:23.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啤…啤水吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,盖子很紧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好厉害 这水是金色的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还一闪一闪的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.00,0:19:49.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那个 我们有带玻璃杯吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该有
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.81,0:19:57.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.68,0:20:03.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就好像月亮溶解在了里面一样
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,气味很独特
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我喝了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.19,0:20:14.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有点苦 又有点甜
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有好多气 感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 再开一瓶吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 先好好想想…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.83,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,-小尤 -怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千疯了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤的脸好有弹性啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这就是月亮的魔力吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看来那水里 果然含有月光啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月光啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.47,0:22:58.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,总有一天 我要爬得高高的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,爬到月亮上去
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好主意 去月亮啊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.58,0:23:07.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那会是个什么样的地方呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.52,0:23:17.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别吃我的头发啊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.39,0:23:22.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,头好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
